To compile these examples, try

cd ~
gcc -o ~/xyplot -I/usr/X11R6/include /usr/share/doc/sciplot-dev/examples/xyplot.c -lsciplot
gcc -o ~/realtime /usr/share/doc/sciplot-dev/examples/realtime.c -lsciplot

To run them, type

xyplot /usr/share/doc/sciplot-dev/examples/data.txt
realtime

This differs somewhat from the instructions in the original package.
The Debian distribution includes the library, libsciplot.so.

